			<p class="fs-6 text">Koh Samui • 4 Rooms</p>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-1">
					<img
						src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/90.jpg"
						class="img-fluid rounded-circle text-center"
						alt=""
						width="75px"
					/>
				</div>
				<div class="col text-start">
					<p class="fs-6 text">Hosted by</p>
					<span>Tony Russo</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p>
				Stylish, tropical, luxurious, airy and absolute stunning view over
				the bay of Chaweng Beach, this villa combines form and function,
				enjoying magnificent views of Samui’s small islands and the sea
				beyond. With 520sqm of indoor/outdoor living space with 7 ensuite
				bedrooms, large living area, infinity pool, garden, air conditioned
				gym, professional pool table, bbq and Sala, this villa is perfect
				for up to 14 adults With 260sqm (2798sqfeet) of living space and
				260sqm of outdoor space.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col">
			<!-- Send host a message section -->
			<div class="border border-start-5 shadow-lg m-4 p-4">
				<h3>$350/night</h3>
				<p>0 Reviews</p>
				<form>
					<div class="mb-3">
						<textarea
							class="form-control"
							placeholder="Send the host a message..."
							rows="6"
						></textarea>
					</div>

					<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-success">
						Request Booking
					</button>
				</form>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="container">
